Reactor Temp Display uses the temperature hud element to display the reactor temp and stability per the options defined below. 

Commands:
  /rtdmode /rtd - Toggle Display mode between 1 and 2.
Mode Examples:
Mode 1:
  HP [60/60  ]
  O2 [100%          ] TM [T:000% | S:000%]
Mode 2:
  When Stability = 100%:
    HP [60/60  ]
    O2 [100%          ] TM [T:000%]
  Or when Stability != 100:
    HP [60/60  ]
    O2 [100%          ] TM [S:000%]
